title: Looking to SpaceX's 2026 IPO
description: Bloomberg Tech co-anchor Ed Ludlow discusses what SpaceX pursuing an IPO in 2026 means for the broader space economy. He joins Vonnie Quinn and Norah Mulinda on Bloomberg Markets. (Source: Bloomberg)
